902
01:19:20.563 --> 01:19:22.100
Yeah.

903
01:19:22.400 --> 01:19:26.167
- Yeah. yeah.
- Just let me look at you.

904
01:19:32.677 --> 01:19:35.152
Your hair came out good.

905
01:19:36.481 --> 01:19:40.887
Look. kid. I'm really bad.
Here. take this gun.

906
01:19:41.687 --> 01:19:44.590
I got nothing better to give ya.
I never gave you anything.

907
01:19:44.690 --> 01:19:47.827
- and now I got nothing to give you.
- Dad. Dad! That is not true.

908
01:19:47.927 --> 01:19:52.163
- I lost ya...
- Dad! Look at me! Look at me!

909
01:19:52.263 --> 01:19:53.966
You did not lose me.

910
01:19:54.066 --> 01:19:58.720
I am not lost. I am right here
with you. okay? Okay?

911
01:19:58.820 --> 01:20:01.733
I'm not gonna leave. Okay?

912
01:20:01.833 --> 01:20:04.129
- Okay.
- Look at me.

913
01:20:04.229 --> 01:20:06.812
- It's just you and me.
- Okay.

914
01:20:06.912 --> 01:20:10.787
I'm not gonna leave. ever. I promise.

915
01:20:12.450 --> 01:20:14.853
You sure are a good girl.

916
01:20:14.953 --> 01:20:18.562
You sure are. You sure are.

917
01:20:21.092 --> 01:20:22.933
Dad?

918
01:20:54.459 --> 01:20:57.493
On your knees! Hands behind your head!

919
01:21:02.233 --> 01:21:05.108
<i>A year ago. I stopped running.</i>

920
01:21:06.104 --> 01:21:10.309
<i>I stopped listening
to all of my worst instincts</i>

921
01:21:10.409 --> 01:21:13.983
<i>and all the worst people.</i>

922
01:21:26.574 --> 01:21:28.960
<i>I'll just tell you this.</i>

923
01:21:29.060 --> 01:21:31.835
I've been sober a year.

924
01:21:33.598 --> 01:21:39.320
I miss my father so much.
that I can't sleep some nights. but...

925
01:21:40.271 --> 01:21:43.050
I tell myself that he's watching over me.

926
01:21:45.843 --> 01:21:47.570
Sometimes.

927
01:21:47.670 --> 01:21:51.001
there's this shame...

928
01:21:51.101 --> 01:21:54.065
that almost breaks my back. but...

929
01:21:54.786 --> 01:21:57.222
I tell myself...

930
01:21:57.322 --> 01:22:01.497
"when you owe your life to someone...

931
01:22:02.110 --> 01:22:04.579
"you better live it."

932
01:22:05.029 --> 01:22:09.072
So. I just say...

933
01:22:11.519 --> 01:22:13.527
<i>"thank you."</i>
